---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FadeUpAnimation from '../components/FadeUpAnimation.astro';
---

<FadeUpAnimation client:load />

<Layout title="Acme Cars">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/acme.css" />

  <div id="body-wrapper">
    <div class="content-small">

      <section class="project-header flex column gap-50">
        <div class="text fade-up">
          <span class="sub-header blue">Acme Cars, 2025</span>
          <h1>
            Upgrading motorcentral’s base dealership website template with a
            modern design and fresh features
          </h1>
        </div>
        <div class="large-image panel-grey fade-up">
          <img src="/images/acme5/acme-hero.jpg" alt="Acme Cars Hero Image" />
        </div>
        <div class="my-role">
          <h2>My role</h2>
          <p>
            As the digital designer on this project, I worked closely with the
            project manager and software development team in order to create a
            design that could work functionally at all screen sizes.
          </p>
          <div class="skills">
            <span>UX/UI Design</span>
            <span>Collaboration</span>
            <span>Prototyping</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="background" class="flex column gap-50">
        <div class="text fade-up">
          <span class="sub-header blue"> Background and problem </span>
          <h2>
            To be able to increase our reach, we needed an overhaul of our
            design
          </h2>
          <p>
            Motorcentral has over has designed and built over 600 websites for
            car dealerships in New Zealand. As you might expect, there comes a
            point where there just aren’t enough clients left locally. Moving
            abroad is the next logical step, but in order to do that, we needed
            to step up or game.
          </p>
          <p>That’s where Acme 5.0 comes in.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="upgrade fade-up">
          <div class="inner panel-grey">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="/images/acme5/old-acme.webp" alt="Old Acme Image" />
            </div>
            <div class="text">
              <span class="sub-header">Old Acme</span>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-x"></span>
                <p>Slow, heavy pages hurting Core Web Vitals</p>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-x"></span>
                <p>Dated look, cramped spacing, weak hierarchy</p>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-x"></span>
                <p>Limited filters made finding cars tedious</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="inner panel-blue">
            <div class="image">
              <img src="/images/acme5/new-acme.webp" alt="New Acme Image" />
            </div>
            <div class="text">
              <span class="sub-header blue">Acme 5.0</span>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-speed"></span>
                <p>Optimised for speed with lighter assets and lazy loading</p>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-design"></span>
                <p>Clear hierarchy, generous spacing, refreshed visuals</p>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-filter"></span>
                <p>More ways to browse: featured, lifestyle, deep filters</p>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-dark"></span>
                <p>Dark mode option that keeps branding intact</p>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-lifestyle"></span>
                <p>Quick lifestyle filters (Family, Adventure, Daily, Work)</p>
              </div>
              <div class="item">
                <span class="icon-ai"></span>
                <p>AI descriptions stay on-brand and surface selling points</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="features" class="flex column gap-50">
        <div class="text fade-up">
          <span class="sub-header blue">Key innovations</span>
          <div class="inner">
            <h2>
              Introducing features that set Acme 5.0 apart from the competition
            </h2>
            <p>
              The latest version of Acme brings powerful new capabilities
              designed to enhance both the customer experience and dealership
              operations. From AI-powered content generation to intuitive search
              functionality, these features represent a significant leap forward
              in automotive website technology.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image-section">
          <div class="image-grid double-column">
            <div class="item panel-grey fade-up">
              <div class="text">
                <h3>
                  Featured vehicle categories to highlight popular choices
                </h3>
                <p>
                  Dealerships can handpick categories like "Hot," "New
                  Arrivals," or "Price Drop" to showcase high-demand vehicles
                  and help customers quickly find popular selections.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="image">
                <img
                  src="/images/acme5/featured.webp"
                  alt="Featured Vehicle Types"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item panel-grey fade-up">
              <div class="text">
                <h3>
                  Making it easier for customers to find their perfect vehicle
                </h3>
                <p>
                  Instead of overwhelming users with technical jargon, Acme 5.0
                  offers lifestyle-oriented categories and intuitive quick
                  filters. Customers can browse by use cases such as family SUV,
                  eco-friendly commuter, or adventure vehicle—getting to their
                  ideal car faster.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="image">
                <img
                  src="/images/acme5/quick-filter.webp"
                  alt="Quick Filter Image"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item panel-grey fade-up">
              <div class="text">
                <h3>
                  Helping customers make informed decisions with intelligent
                  vehicle summaries
                </h3>
                <p>
                  AI-generated descriptions automatically highlight key features
                  and selling points for each vehicle. This saves dealerships
                  hours of manual content creation while ensuring consistent,
                  high-quality information.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="image">
                <img
                  src="/images/acme5/ai-summary.webp"
                  alt="Acme Cars AI Summary"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item panel-grey fade-up">
              <div class="text">
                <h3>Easily switch between Cash and Finance pricing views</h3>
                <p>
                  Customers can toggle between cash and finance pricing with a
                  single click, allowing them to quickly assess affordability
                  options without navigating away from the vehicle listing.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="image">
                <img
                  src="/images/acme5/finance-switcher.webp"
                  alt="Acme Cars Pricing Toggle"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="example-websites flex column gap-50">
        <div class="text fade-up">
          <span class="sub-header blue">Acme 5.0 forks</span>
          <h2>Real dealerships using Acme 5.0 across New Zealand</h2>
          <p>
            After designing the Acme 5.0 template, I built and deployed these
            websites for dealerships throughout New Zealand. Each site is
            customized to match the dealer's brand while maintaining the core
            features and user experience of the Acme template.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="website-list fade-up">
          <a
            href="https://feildingmotorgroup.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>feildingmotorgroup.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://autolinecars.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>autolinecars.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://wiltoncars.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>wiltoncars.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://shoreprestige.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>shoreprestige.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://clickcars.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>clickcars.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://futuremotors.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>futuremotors.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://planetcars.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>planetcars.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://kiwiaffordablecars.co.nz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="panel-hover"
          >
            <p>kiwiaffordablecars.co.nz</p>
            <span class="icon-open"></span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
